name: CubeVoid
description:
This is a dev build of my mobile game CubeVoid.

Tap left/right side of screen to avoid cubes, collect energy cells/packs to keep alive.

Assets from unity asset store aside from a few sound effects and the main menu music I composed.

This is an APK file that will need to be downloaded to an android device to play, I have not tested it in bluestacks.

Thanks for stopping by and checking out CubeVoid!
